sg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11e456f61869edb34c5bcfcf26f41ca89f66c8ee","tid":1610739,"uid":178066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:13:02.000Z","msg":"最好既方法係同信得過既人組小隊<br />\n打遊擊"},{"pid":"fcb91636ef18c245e5edbc31b98970a5d9d78a0d","tid":1610739,"uid":240242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:15:51.000Z","msg":"哨兵不足/亂指揮都係死因<br />\n有時前線同後排都係因為獲得既訊息不一致而引起誤會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以後大家都要面皮厚啲 主動同身邊人溝通 再前後大叫互通消息"},{"pid":"e304e1e12b2e9196e541a3de0ce944149db9d532","tid":1610739,"uid":238920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:22:26.000Z","msg":"太多人企埋一邊睇,冇實質參與<br />\n你和理非出到場唔落手落腳,都幫幫手傳下物資做下哨兵<br />\n企係中間無撚啦啦大叫阿~~~~~<br />\n下一秒唱死黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"102b7f8ba00051c4176fa900753b14ff56a07928","tid":1610739,"uid":269096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:26:30.000Z","msg":"其實大家多行一步就好好多：<br />\n<br />\n中後線咪撚發夢用手機，留意現場手足指示，製造物資，要人個陣唔該真係向前行。要你退都留意指示退。<br />\n<br />\n前線有咩需要，即刻叫後面畀，咪撚用人鏈，自己跑9過去畀前線。"},{"pid":"aa76161aa8e348ffc4fb69f3b1a9de0cc06337fc","tid":1610739,"uid":270687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:28:44.000Z","msg":"非常認同，好多時大家對fight or flight既criteria係完全0溝通，唔好講共識，連大聲講出黎都無，要等到黑警郁手先開始討論<br />\n<br />\n淨係靠個人覺悟，我覺得係另一種教條主義"},{"pid":"894d6597cf92ca10ca6e6c833290941efceda59c","tid":1610739,"uid":96146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:29:36.000Z","msg":"好多和理非連製作魔法液都唔敢<br />\n<br />\n但求佢地幫手帶d原材料 我地自行製造<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"869afac6028dfa58a7f0903add39155b923df5a1","tid":1610739,"uid":270687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e304e1e12b2e9196e541a3de0ce944149db9d532","tid":1610739,"uid":238920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T